  <front>
    <title>ALTO cellular addresses</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-randriamasy-alto-cellular-adresses-02"/>
    <author initials="S." surname="Randriamasy" fullname="Sabine Randriamasy">
      <organization>Nokia-Bell-labs</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="05" month="March" year="2018"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This draft proposes to use the cellular address format composed of
   elements as specified by 3GPP and called ECGI.  ECGI stands for
   E-UTRAN Cell Global Identifier and is used in Public Land Mobile
   Networks based on E-UTRAN.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
</reference>